title: Ebro In The Morning - Chicken Wing Shortage: Real or Fake?
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/23. 

Many politicians played themselves (16:00), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (7:00, & 32:02), and the crew discusses the great Chicken Wing Shortage (43:00). Gurus at 56 minutes.
